In [35]:
mean_budget = df['budget'].mean()
df['budget'].fillna(mean_budget, inplace=True)

mean_gross = df['gross'].mean()
df['gross'].fillna(mean_gross, inplace=True)

mode_rating = df['rating'].mode()[0]
df['rating'].fillna(mode_rating, inplace=True)
